          <briefdescription>
<para>Reflect the entity&apos;s velocity off the collision surface. </para>
          </briefdescription>
          <detaileddescription>
<para>Uses the surface normal to calculate a reflected velocity vector. Commonly used for projectiles bouncing off walls. </para>
          </detaileddescription>
